The paper discusses the limitations of cooperation in wireless systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the impact of cooperation on system performance, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper uses examples from cellular systems (cs.MM) and discusses the impact of transmit power on system performance (cs.CE).
